General.Name: Minbos Resources Ltd
General.Description: Minbos Resources Limited engages in the exploration and development of mineral projects. The company explores for phosphate and ammonia deposits. It focuses on the development of the Capanda Green Ammonia Project and the Cabinda Phosphate Project in Angola and middle Africa. Minbos Resources Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Subiaco, Australia.
